                "manifests itself as a peak in the reaction yield",
                "distribution versus the relative energy of two neutrons"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The nn scattering length ann was determined by",
                "comparing the experimentally measured yield of the",
                "neutron-deuteron breakup reaction with the",
                "ann-dependent results of a simulation in the",
                "Migdal-Watson approximation for deltaANGLE = 6 deg and",
                "En=40+-5 MeV. See also Fig.3 of J,JP/CS,340,012047,2012"
              ]
